---
import Container from "@/components/ui/Container.astro";
---

<section class="bg-nude py-20 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <Container>
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-sage font-medium mb-3 reveal">TRAYECTORIA</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-serif text-charcoal mb-4 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        Experiencia Profesional
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-[2px] bg-sage mx-auto reveal reveal-delay-2"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Formación en promoción del bienestar emocional y prevención de problemáticas psicológicas a nivel individual y grupal.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/experience/psicoeducacion.png" alt="Psicoeducación en salud mental" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-charcoal group-hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-300">
            Psicoeducación en Salud Mental
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Sensibilización y acompañamiento en prevención de violencia con niños, adolescentes y familias.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/experience/prevencion_violencia.png" alt="Prevención en violencia" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-charcoal group-hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-300">
            Prevención en Violencia
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Juego terapéutico, dibujo y técnicas adaptadas al desarrollo infantil con enfoque respetuoso.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/experience/trabajo_ninos.jpg" alt="Trabajo con niños" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-charcoal group-hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-300">
            Trabajo con Niños
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Investigación en desarrollo infantil temprano en contextos interculturales de la sierra ecuatoriana.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/experience/investigacion.jpg" alt="Investigación" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-charcoal group-hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-300">
            Investigación Clínica
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-stone-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 reveal reveal-delay-5">
        <div class="relative h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-end p-6">
            <p class="text-white text-sm leading-relaxed">Rotaciones en neonatología, pediatría y obstetricia de alto riesgo. Acompañamiento en duelo perinatal.</p>
          </div>
          <img src="/images/experience/clinica_hospitalaria.png" alt="Clínica hospitalaria" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-charcoal group-hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-300">
            Clínica Hospitalaria
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
